e Velocity artifact does not make JDOM available on this test classpath, so the dedicated `NodeListTest` needs the matching JDOM test dependency even though the test itself does not directly use JDOM classes.\n\nI did not run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01eccaeb11aae595016a033108ab74819d9ebfeb095e4c4f82\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 620, "output": 700, "cacheRead": 35328, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 36648, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778594045407, "responseId": "resp_01eccaeb11aae595016a0330fe23bc819da07bf45084243fb8"}, "toolResults": []}
